Convert-PerlRef2String version 0.03
===================================

This is a handy tool for who wants to exchange PERL references over the Internet as compressed strings. 
When both the sender and receiver are PERL programs you can use this tool as an alternative to 
exchanging XML files (sometimes this methods is more powerful than SOAP).


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

 MIME::Base64
 Compress::Zlib
 Data::Dumper


